    "faq-section": {
      "type": "faq-section",
      "blocks": {
        "collapsible_row_DCpttL": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Do your fragrances smell the same as the designer inspiration?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Our fragrances are expertly crafted to capture the essence and character of popular designer scents. While we create inspired interpretations rather than exact copies, 98% of our customers say our<br/>fragrances are virtually identical to the original brands they love. Each fragrance is carefully developed to deliver the same luxurious experience at a fraction of the cost.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_3dNyaD": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How can I trust the quality at the price point you offer?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>We cut out the middleman and brand markup, not the quality.<br/>Our fragrances are made in Canada using high concentrations of premium fragrance oils, the same quality ingredients found in luxury brands. We're so confident in our products that we offer a 60-day money-back guarantee. Plus, thousands of 5-star reviews from happy customers speak to our consistent<br/>quality.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_p7jMRw": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How long will the scent last?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Our Eau de Parfum formulations contain high concentrations of quality fragrance oils, typically lasting 12+ hours on the skin. Longevity can vary based on skin type, application method, and individual body chemistry. For best results, apply to pulse points on clean, moisturized skin.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_TGd86r": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": " Are your products vegan friendly and cruelty free?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>We only use <strong>vegan-friendly</strong> fragrance oils, and of course they are <strong>cruelty-free</strong>! We wouldn't have it any other way. Smell good, feel good, do good.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_GixNBx": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I return/exchange if I don't like the scent?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Yes. We offer a 60-day money-back guarantee. If you're not<br/>completely satisfied with your fragrance, simply return it within 60 days for a<br/>full refund. You can even test the fragrance once or twice before deciding. No<br/>questions asked, no hassle.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_6xgRnc": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Are your fragrances safe for sensitive skin?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Our fragrances are formulated to high safety standards, but like all fragrances, they may contain allergens. We recommend patch testing before full use, especially if you have sensitive skin. All ingredients comply with international safety regulations for cosmetic products.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
      },
